# Verification

After non-trivial code changes:

1. Run **`npm run ci`** from repo root when frontend or root scripts change.
2. Run **`cd backend && make test`** when backend Python changes (requires deps: `pip install -r backend/requirements.txt`).
3. Prefer **`npm run verify`** for an end-to-end local gate when both areas matter.

If checks fail, fix or report—do not claim success without running them or explaining the skip.

Canonical runtime versions: **`.nvmrc`**, **`backend/.python-version`**, and **`.github/workflows/ci.yml`**.
